> Problem is that in some states, like TN, different municipalities have
> different smog regs.  So they prevent you from registering in other
> counties to get around them.  A lot of that was going on here before
> they banned it.  Chattanooga was going to lose a lot of federal money
> unless they started emissions testing.  But then TVA is burning coal by
> the metric megaton to keep the power on.  Cheers....KR
